{"tid":810471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【屌動物】野生河狸被撞重傷 還慘遭男子性侵亡","createTime":"2018-09-08T04:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T05:12:34.000Z","uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1c1e1c9dc911443376d46d8e3a5d680062d63559","tid":810471,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:15:25.000Z","msg":"美國一名男子遭控性侵河狸（beaver），週一遭當局逮捕，以虐待動物罪名起訴。<br />\n<br />\n華盛頓州肯納威克（Kennewick）一名女子行經哥倫比亞公園（Columbia Park），驚見一隻河狸被車撞傷。她趕緊跑回家拿箱子，準備帶河狸去給獸醫檢查。但她拿著箱子回到現場時，卻看見一名男子在河狸身旁。起初她以為男子是在安撫河狸，沒想到仔細一看，男子竟脫下褲子，身體壓在河狸上方。警方到場時，河狸已傷重身亡。<br />\n警方表示，他們接獲舉報，哥倫比亞公園一名男子與野生動物進行短暫性接觸。該男子是35歲的戴納（Richard Delp），以虐待動物及持有毒品安非他命等罪名被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180907/58654845\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F58654845&d=9xv0JFbQRmkqdytgjbZEH3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e4cb69bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F58654845&h=ee03fd42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180907/58654845</a>"},{"pid":"a9521d507e648f956364f8cc62c304caece7dcb7","tid":810471,"uid":28504,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:17:27.000Z","msg":"吊狸咩....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cadab27b3cd2690681c811a56e6bf1d20453ecc4","tid":810471,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9521d507e648f956364f8cc62c304caece7dcb7","tid":810471,"uid":28504,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:17:27.000Z","msg":"吊狸咩....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:18:44.000Z","msg":"一名男性河狸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9655267c0ce97200aef7d